The Man Who Wasn't There;;85;;81;;R;;A dark tale of infidelity and murder, crime and punishment. Set in a small northern California town of the late 40s, the film portrays Ed Crane (Billy Bob Thornton), a barber dissatisfied with his life. His wife Doris' (Frances McDormand) infidelity presents Ed with an opportunity for blackmail that he thinks will help him to change it. However, Ed's scheme unravels and lays bare even darker secrets...;;Drama,Crime;;Joel Coen;;2001;;Billy Bob Thornton,Frances McDormand,Michael Badalucco,James Gandolfini,Katherine Borowitz,Jon Polito,Scarlett Johansson,Richard Jenkins,Tony Shalhoub,Adam Alexi-Malle;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/man_who_wasnt_there